reviewText: The accompanying book was a complete piece of photocopied crap. It would have been REALLY nice to have a list of materials and a nice drawing to copy for each painting.
What an excellent instruction DVD. I can't wait to get some more of the collection! Very reasonably priced and very fast shipping.

The DVD's by S. Schewee seem to be easy enough to follow. I have not actually done a painting yet. The vendor was very quick to correct a problem with one of the DVD's. I really appreciated the service from this vendor.
